music playback is realized through music player daemon, so mpd and mpc should be installed and configured.

MPD Guide: http://mpd.wikia.com/wiki/Configuration
mpd --create-db
/etc/init.d/mpd restart

pyhton libs needed:

eyed3
cheetah
webpy

initial setup:
run python createMusicLib.py /path/to/music or set your path in the settings.py
to create the music database

change variable musicfolder in settings.py to /path/to/your/music
should be the same path you used in the createMusicLib

run python webpy.py
access webinterface via http://localhost:8080/
vote songs and have fun!
